      "value": "<p>You maintain your combat prowess even when at a disadvantage.</p>\n<p><strong>Prerequisites</strong>: Str 11.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Benefit</strong>: The normal penalties to attack rolls from being @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.conditions.Item.4AkWDHGM6gHDepHN]{Grappled}, @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.conditions.Item.XgK4EdO5D3Fj3iWz]{Pinned}, and @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.conditions.Item.XeRGqHVtcZ7vsgJ0]{Prone} don’t apply to your unarmed attacks. The penalties from the @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.conditions.Item.XgK4EdO5D3Fj3iWz]{Pinned} condition don’t apply to your attempts to grapple your opponent or free yourself.</p>"
